text:
이 때도 항상 옛날을 그리워 했던 것 같다
그 시절의 이제 느끼지 못 할 특별한 열 세 남자들의 청춘을 담은 노래를 언제 다시 듣게 될 줄 모르겠다
옛을 그리워 하 던 그 때가 이젠 그리워 지는 걸 봐서는 지금의 힘들었던 하루하루도 언젠가 우리에게 돌아가고 싶어지는 추억으로 남게 될 지 모르겠다
지금 이 청춘이라는 느낌이 언제 다시 찾아올지 모르겠고 지금 내가 살아가는 시간을 아끼고 그리워 할 만큼 보람차게 살아나가는게 제일 멋있는거 같다
난 이 때의 감성 분위기가 너무 소중하고 또 소중하다 언제나 사랑해 세븐틴 ❤ !

author: @ektasingh4452
text:
a
1 year ago (edited)
SVT INSIDE JOKES PREFERENCES:

0:08 - (the8 as hoshi) hoshi's ambitious speech everytime he leads the cheer before svt goes on stage
0:51 - (mingyu as scoups) scoups' habit of biting members when he gets shy
0:55 - (scoups as mingyu) mingyu's habit of rolling his tongue out whenever the cam points to him
1:06 - (hoshi as seungkwan) seungkwan's habit of slightly raising his arms with his wrists kinda folded & his excessive love for iced americano
1:18 - (joshua as jun) jun always having his eyes glued to his phone whenever theyre off stage
1:26 - (vernon as woozi) woozi being addicted to working out every single day & his iconic slippers that he wears 24/7
1:39 - (wonwoo as vernon) vernon's signature move that he made for left n right stages
1:48 - (woozi as dino) dino's iconic electric shaver story that woozi told (basically dino used to drink often and he'll always leave at midnight then return the next morning drunk af, he will then start to electric shave as his way to sober up)
2:05 - (jeonghan as the8) the8's hobby to meditate & his love for wine (the8 has a wine ref & wine bottle collection in his room)
2:18 - (scoups as mingyu) mingyu's clumsy ass and scoups scolding him for it (there was NOT a day where mingyu dont trip, spill food/water, or break glasses as members stated)
2:24 - (jun as joshua) joshua's audition that turned into meme where he played his guitar and sang sunday morning
2:35 -(woozi as dino) woozi imitating dino's powerful and precised moves
2:43 - (dk as jeonghan) jeonghan's 'always tired' pose (he gets tired easily bc he has low stamina)
2:54 - (dino as dk) another iconic dk & mingyu plastic bag story (there was one time dk & mingyu were arguing but dk just got home from the convience store so he was holding a plastic bag. as they argue, dk threw the plastic bag at the floor which made mingyu angrier & said "pick it up, arent u going to pick it up?" so dk ended up picking it up bc he was scared mingyu might hit him (theyre the same age btw which made this story funnier)
3:05 - (the8 as hoshi) hoshi's tiger agenda (hoshi kept pushing that he looks like a tiger and even owns an insane amount of tiger stuff (plushies, watch, shoes, caps, phone case, clothes) and he LITERALLY thinks that hes a whole ass tiger not a human
3:12 - (scoups as mingyu) mingyu's tall ass height
3:13 - (mingyu as scoups) scoups way of posing for selfies
3:23 - (seungkwan as wonwoo) wonwoo's deep ass mc voice on gose logic night ep
3:35 - (jun as joshua) this is what joshua shows whenever hes asked whats his special skill
3:44 - (dino as dk) the udon scream story (in that one 'if' ep, dk was doing whats in the box challenge bc he lost in a game. there was an udon inside the box and when he slightly touched it, he got so scared that he screamed and run up to the wall while raising his hand (the way they were doing it here) for like a whole min)

author: @shielamaycalo295
text:
In true SEVENTEEN fashion, the group took things a step further than the typical part-switch dance video: instead of just swapping parts, each of the members made a complete transformation into the member that he was covering, imitating his mannerisms and even referencing some inside jokes that fans will recognize immediately.

Highlights of the video include Hoshi pretending to be knocked to the ground by a flying kick from Seungkwan, Jun and Joshua acting out a physical altercation involving a ukulele, S.Coups tripping over a meditating Jeonghan, DK and The8 rubbing their chests together in an overly affectionate hug, Woozi pretending to shave Dino’s face, and Mingyuconstantly attempting to bite the other members.

Towards the end of the clip, Joshua and Dino also hilariously act out the infamous “black plastic bag” fight between DK and Mingyu, with Dino angrily throwing a plastic bag on the floor, then sheepishly complying when Joshua orders him to pick it up.



-Soompi

author: @mymyleechan1607
text:
S.Coups [imitating Mingyu]: imitating his tall height + clumsiness (tripping over Jeonghan)

Jeonghan [imitating The8]: imitating his calm nature (meditating) + love for wine

Joshua [imitating Jun]: imitating his sleepy appearance + habit of always being on his phone + saying “naju nice”

Jun [imitating Joshua]: imitating his talent for playing the guitar + singing “Sunday Morning” (by Maroon 5) + his “pin drop” dance move

Hoshi [imitating Seungkwan]: imitating his unique hand gestures/body movements + his love for iced Americanos + him dancing to girl group songs + his iconic wink before the chorus

Wonwoo [imitating Vernon]: imitating the time when he wore red-colored glasses and couldn’t read red-colored writing (wearing purple-colored glasses) + the way he dances + slow turtle Vernon™

Woozi [imitating Dino]: imitating the time he was on a razor advertisement (also exaggerating his dance movements a lil lol)

The8 [imitating Hoshi]: imitating his high energy level + Hoshi tiger agenda (mimicking tiger claws with his hands) + his dance in his collab with Woozi, “Bring It”

Mingyu [imitating S.Coups]: imitating his tendency to bite the members’ shoulders when he laughs/cringes + his habit of scolding the members as the leader + the way he takes selfies

DK [imitating Jeonghan]: imitating his easy-going personality & tendency to get tired easily + tendency to play along with Hoshi’s antics (such as saying he is a tiger)

Seungkwan [imitating Wonwoo]: imitating the way his mouth moves when singing + his emceeing in the “Debate Night” Going Seventeen episodes

Vernon [imitating Woozi] imitating how he’s always working out + constantly wearing slippers

Dino [imitating DK]: imitating the time when he got angry with Mingyu and threw a plastic bag at the floor then Mingyu told him to pick it up and he actually did lololol + the time he crazily waved his hand on the wall after being scared by trying to guess what was inside of a box

author: @moreenannee
text:
SVT INSIDE JOKES PREFERENCES:

0:08 - (the8 as hoshi) hoshi's ambitious speech everytime he leads the cheer before svt goes on stage
0:51 - (mingyu as scoups) scoups' habit of biting members when he gets shy
0:55 - (scoups as mingyu) mingyu's habit of rolling his tongue out whenever the cam points to him
1:06 - (hoshi as seungkwan) seungkwan's habit of slightly raising his arms with his wrists kinda folded & his excessive love for iced americano
1:18 - (joshua as jun) jun always having his eyes glued to his phone whenever theyre off stage
1:26 - (vernon as woozi) woozi being addicted to working out every single day & his iconic slippers that he wears 24/7
1:39 - (wonwoo as vernon) vernon's signature move that he made for left n right stages
1:48 - (woozi as dino) dino's iconic electric shaver story that woozi told (basically dino used to drink often and he'll always leave at midnight then return the next morning drunk af, he will then start to electric shave as his way to sober up)
2:05 - (jeonghan as the8) the8's hobby to meditate & his love for wine (the8 has a wine ref & wine bottle collection in his room)
2:18 - (scoups as mingyu) mingyu's clumsy ass and scoups scolding him for it (there was NOT a day where mingyu dont trip, spill food/water, or break glasses as members stated)
2:24 - (jun as joshua) joshua's audition that turned into meme where he played his guitar and sang sunday morning
2:35 -(woozi as dino) woozi imitating dino's powerful and precised moves
2:43 - (dk as jeonghan) jeonghan's 'always tired' pose (he gets tired easily bc he has low stamina)
2:54 - (dino as dk) another iconic dk & mingyu plastic bag story (there was one time dk & mingyu were arguing but dk just got home from the convience store so he was holding a plastic bag. as they argue, dk threw the plastic bag at the floor which made mingyu angrier & said "pick it up, arent u going to pick it up?" so dk ended up picking it up bc he was scared mingyu might hit him (theyre the same age btw which made this story funnier)
3:05 - (the8 as hoshi) hoshi's tiger agenda (hoshi kept pushing that he looks like a tiger and even owns an insane amount of tiger stuff (plushies, watch, shoes, caps, phone case, clothes) and he LITERALLY thinks that hes a whole ass tiger not a human
3:12 - (scoups as mingyu) mingyu's tall ass height
3:13 - (mingyu as scoups) scoups way of posing for selfies
3:23 - (seungkwan as wonwoo) wonwoo's deep ass mc voice on gose logic night ep
3:35 - (jun as joshua) this is what joshua shows whenever hes asked whats his special skill
3:44 - (dino as dk) the udon scream story (in that one 'if' ep, dk was doing whats in the box challenge bc he lost in a game. there was an udon inside the box and when he slightly touched it, he got so scared that he screamed and run up to the wall while raising his hand (the way they were doing it here) for like a whole min)

ure welcome

author: @doremifasolasiyeon9005
text:
for the references :D
0:05 minghao as hoshi who often leads the cheer backstage before svt starts their performance.
0:41 wonu as vernon wearing vernon style glasses, jeonghan as minghao holding a wine glass bc hao likes wines (svt club)
0:50 mingyu as seungcheol who has a habit of biting svt members when he's flustered or excited.
1:06 hoshi as seungkwan, copying his gestures when he talks while holding iced coffee americano (seungkwan's fav) seungkwan kicks him (um arent u supposed to be copying wonu)
1:22 joshua as jun who is always facing his phone and jun as joshua who likes to play the guitar and sing sunday morning.
1:25 vernon as woozi whose hobby is working out
1:34 minghao as hoshi, doing a heart sign bc hoshi does that a lot
1:41 wonu as vernon, vernon's weird dance move that he did in sbs gayo daejun 2019 (?) as well as in l&r choreo.
2:07 jeonghan as minghao, idk about this but they once jokingly challenged minghao to try meditating. idk he must be learning to meditate recently. he seems like that kind of guy lol. 
2:17 seungcheol as CLUMSY mingyu. fun fact: mingyu trips EVERYDAY. 
2:35 woozi as dino copying his PASSIONATE dance
2:45 dk as jeonghan who like to sleep when he finds an opportunity. he said that he can sleep everywhere.
2:51 vernon as woozi, holding a dumbbell cus woozi likes to workout
2:55 dino as dk, throwing his hat. in gose insomnia ep, they said dk throws things when he's angry. he threw a gray towel at seungkwan and he threw a black plastic bag at mingyu who told him to pick it up, which dk really did picked it up
3:06 minghao imitating hoshi's tiger agenda
3:09 woozi shaving dino's nonexistent beard. in insomnia gose ep, he joked about dino shaving after getting drunk the night before. also, back in rookie days, a member saw dino shaving for the first time and dino got flustered by it. 
3:13 seungcheol emphasizing mingyu's height and seungkwan as wonwoo copying his robot-like dance. wonu is a *dance machine* wbk.
3:14 mingyu as seungcheol, copying the way he takes selfies with people.
3:28 seungkwan as MC wonu (particularly debate night gose ep)
3:36 woozi (as dino) shaves minghao (as hoshi) who's dancing to bring it (by hoshwoozi combo) choreo
3:43 dino and dk copying dk's weird hand thing (?) in "if" episode when he got scared and shookt by the hidden box
3:45 joshua and jun, joshua's weird....talent that he flexed many times before.
there's so much going on so i probably missed loads of things.
for new stans, ya'll should try watch going seventeen,svt club,  one fine day, inside seventeen and hit the road. if you don't feel mentally well, don't watch hit the road. it's basically a documentary of the boys showing their vulnerable side.
